Package: genderstat
Type: Package
Title: genderstat: Quantitative Analysis Tools for Gender Studies
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Mashrur Ayon mashrur399@gmail.com
Maintainer: Mashrur Ayon <mashrur399@gmail.com>
Description: Genderstat is an R package designed to provide tools for quantitative analysis in gender studies. It includes functions to calculate various gender inequality metrics, such as the Gender Pay Gap, Gender Inequality Index (GII), Gender Development Index (GDI), Occupational Segregation Indices, Gender Empowerment Measure (GEM), and Time-use Analysis Metrics. The package also offers sample datasets for practice and learning purposes.
